goals__remit:
GMIT aims to provide our students with a transformative university experience, empowering our graduates to fully contribute to the social, economic and cultural betterment of society. GMIT is a nurturing institution that helps foster the capabilities and creativity of a diverse student and staff community in their intellectual, personal and social endeavours. In providing students with this transformative university experience GMIT: 
•    Enables access and opportunity for a diverse student community; 
•    Attracts, supports and encourages highly talented staff; 
•    Maintains positive staff-student interactions; 
•    Invests in innovative research and applied teaching and learning; 
•    Collaborates with government, agencies, enterprise and the community; 
•    Develops confident, professional, knowledgeable and skilled graduates equipped to contribute as global citizens.
